I would take us outside

00:00:17.160 --> 00:00:20.520
except for the whole recording business,

00:00:20.520 --> 00:00:23.370
which we can't take outside,

00:00:23.370 --> 00:00:27.840
which makes me a little sad
because it's a beautiful day.

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:29.640
This has been one of
those New England falls

00:00:29.640 --> 00:00:31.920
that they promise you with the nice days

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:34.230
and, like, the leaves
falling from the trees.

